Package io.swagger.v3.oas.annotations.info

Annotation Type Info

  • @Target(ANNOTATION_TYPE)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Inherited
public @interface Info
    The annotation may be used in OpenAPIDefinition.info() to populate the Info section of the OpenAPI document.
    See Also:
    Info (OpenAPI specification), Info (OpenAPI specification), OpenAPIDefinition
